com.mojang.datafixers.schemas

Class Schema

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mojang.datafixers.schemas.Schema

  • public class Schema
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents a bunch of data types. Do not directly create a new Schema, you need to extend the schema with your own custom one. Then, add your types in the appropriate methods in the child class.
    Since:
    1.0.19
